\pard\pardeftab720\sa320\partightenfactor0

\fs32 \cf4 \cb3 Please clone the repo available at {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://github.com/professordiogodev/multi-tier-ingress-eks-lab"}}{\fldrslt 
\f1 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF65539 \cf5 https://github.com/professordiogodev/multi-tier-ingress-eks-lab}}\cb1 \

\f2\b \cb3 Assumption:
\f0\b0  Your EKS cluster is already configured and your 
\f3 kubectl
\f0  context points to it.\cb1 \

\f2\b \cb3 Repo (after clone):
\f0\b0 \cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f3 \cf6 \cb7 .\
\uc0\u9500 \u9472 \u9472  backend\
