\f2\b \cf4 \cb3 Goal:
\f0\b0  Deploy the two-tier app (frontend 
\f4 \uc0\u8594 
\f0  backend) to 
\f2\b EKS
\f0\b0  using an 
\f2\b Ingress
\f0\b0 , and expose it via 
\f2\b Route 53
\f0\b0  at 
\f3 http://app.<your-name>.diogohack.shop
\f0 .\cb1 \

\f5\i \cb3 Pick a 
\f6\b unique
\f5\b0  
\f7 <your-name>
\f5  (lowercase, no spaces), e.g. 
\f7 diogo
\f5 , 
\f7 marta
\f5 , 
\f7 joao
\f5 . We\'92ll also isolate resources per student using a personal namespace.\cb1 \

